	<!-- TEXT  -->
	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_GEYSER_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Pretty Cool-dera</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_GEYSER_HELP">
			<Text>Greetings to Your Majesty. I bring a report from our man stationed at the Geyser. The Yellowstone Caldera has been seeing some unusual activity recently, and he is looking for advice on how to proceed.[NEWLINE]What shall I write, Your Grace?</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_GEYSER_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>The Natural Wonder permenantly yields +1 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science, [ICON_TOURISM] Tourism and [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_GEYSER_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>At the expense of -5 [ICON_FOOD] Food per turn, all nearby Camps provide +1 [ICON_GOLD] Gold and you receive a copy of [ICON_RES_FUR] Furs.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_GEYSER_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Regulations reduce the [ICON_PRODUCTION] of nearby Lumbermills by -1. In return, the Natural Wonder yields +6 [ICON_FOOD] Food.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_GEYSER_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Investigating the various phenomena of The Caldera allows any Research Lab, Medical Lab or Spaceship Factory present in the City to generate +5 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_GEYSER_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>These disturbances he describes must have a rational explanation, see to it we find them.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_GEYSER_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>*The correspondance goes into depth about trappers who have set up camp in the region*[NEWLINE]The culling of nature is sometimes necessary, if our current populations can take the hit, I'd like to see how much this development could benefit the hunting industry locally.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_GEYSER_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>*Logging ventures in the local regions infringe on The Caldera, threatening natural habitats*[NEWLINE]Place restrictions on how much these loggers can chop, we must ensure such a bountiful resource is not damaged, accidentally or otherwise.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_NW_GEYSER_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>*Modern scientific techniques have discovered much in the region, from the small to the... disastrously large*[NEWLINE]This is excellent news, once again Nature inspires us to higher things!</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
</GameData>